    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 6th level, your patron’s powers have a profound effect on your body and magic. You don’t need to eat, drink, or breathe.</p>\n<p>In addition, once during each of your turns, when you hit a creature with an attack and roll damage against the creature, you can replace the damage type with <strong>necrotic damage</strong>. While you are using your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.e1orFuja4KP25lol]{Form of Dread}, you can roll one additional damage die when determining the necrotic damage the target takes.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: This feature is set up with options to roll a d6 or a d8 of necrotic damage. Make changes according to whichever dice you use most.</em></p>\n</section>",
